Package: ggfan
Type: Package
Title: Summarise A Distribution Through Coloured Intervals
Description: Implements the functionality of the fanplot package as ggplot
  geoms. Designed for summarising MCMC samples from a posterior distribution,
  where a visualisation is desired for several values of a continuous covariate.
  Increasing posterior intervals of the sampled quantity are mapped to a continuous colour 
  scale.
Version: 0.1.0   
